org.spongepowered.api.text.translation

Interface Translation


  • public interface Translation
    A Translation most closely represents any given Minecraft translation ID. It allows for getting a string of text in multiple locales in the client; however, it is mostly used to hold a translation ID when sending a message so the client can do translation. Some Translations have parameters, and some do not.

    On the server-side, the only available locale is English.
